---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">
  <section class="page">
    <h1>Our Services</h1>
    <p>We provide a wide range of automotive services for most makes and models.</p>

    <ul class="services-list">
      <li><strong>Oil Changes</strong> — Quick lube and filter replacement using quality oils.</li>
      <li><strong>Brake Service</strong> — Pads, rotors, and full brake system inspections.</li>
      <li><strong>Diagnostics</strong> — Check engine light, electrical troubleshooting, and ECU scans.</li>
      <li><strong>Transmission</strong> — Fluid service, diagnostics, and repairs.</li>
      <li><strong>Suspension</strong> — Shocks, struts, alignment checks, and repairs.</li>
      <li><strong>Tires</strong> — Rotation, balancing, and replacement.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
